I am skeptical since we had to translate one format to another, neither of which we control. Those are moving targets. Since there is already `kompose`, I would prefer to leave it up to this tool to support translating compose files into K8s yaml.

In other words, I'd appreciate if we wouldn't have to support this scenario; once something has merged, we effectively support it.

@containers/podman-maintainers PTAL
